      <title>中东紧张局势和中国政策乐观情绪推动油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-24</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列对黎巴嫩发动空袭，造成近 500 人死亡并加剧了地区紧张局势，油价小幅上涨，而中国当局准备举行吹风会，引发对出台更多刺激措施的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-24</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 23:36:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
